Hansjoerg (Jacky) Baltes教授


1.University of Manitoba教授，世界盃機器人比賽RoboCup與FIRA執行委員兼副主席
2. University of Calgary博士
http://www.cs.umanitoba.ca/~jacky/


1. Introduction to localization and mapping for navigation.
2. The fundamentals of probability theory for Localization and mapping.
3. Localization: motion models, sensor models, and Monte Carlo method, particle filter.
4. Eigenvectors and singular value decomposition.
5. Incremental closest point algorithm. 
6. Introduction to computer vision, thresholding, histograms, edge detection, Sobel, and Laplacian.
7. Convolution, segmentation, and integral image.
8. Visual SLAM, SIFT and SURF features.
9. Visual SLAM - Bundle adjustment.




 
 
 
